title: S with Annie but no Mastery Token
body:
Hiya

I just played what I felt was my best game with Annie, and I got an S rating. But for some reason, even though I am Mastery 5 on Annie, I didn't get a Mastery 6 Token.

Is this some sort of bug, or something?

Thanks :)

replies.body: Were you level 5 mastery prior to the match where you earned an S- or above?
That doesnt make a difference? I got an S for Lux and Nid at level 4 and got box and w.e, but my Kassadin got an S+ and nothing happened for him
